Summary: Light in sky spotted looking over Manchester city centre.
divs: Sighting DetailsI took this photo as I could not identify the object as an aircraft. This was taken looking North East from my house into the sky over Manchester city centre. It did not move and was in the sky for around 30 minutes. I would just like to know if anything like this has been seen anywheere before of if it can be explained. I remain open minded!
